{"tid":1390460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯署: 阻止曾偉雄被任命為聯合國維也納辦事處總幹事！","createTime":"2019-07-31T06:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T15:05:38.000Z","uid":93905,"like":193,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"3b168f2ab685825a7e2a8983386f6216959e269a","tid":1390460,"uid":93905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:53:55.000Z","msg":"請廣傳！！阻止曾偉雄被任命為聯合國維也納辦事處總幹事！<br />\n<br />\n現為中國國家禁毒委員會副主任的前任香港警務處長「禿鷹」曾偉雄，已獲國家提名，競逐聯合國維也納辦事處(UNOV)總幹事、暨聯合國毒品和犯罪問題辦公室(UNODC)行政總監這「二合一」職位。警察濫暴，隨意向市民投催淚彈鎮壓，始於曾偉雄。請大家在國際社會發聲，阻止曾偉雄當選！<br />\n<br />\n聯署請往（記得要確認電郵，簽署方能成功）:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=35973e28\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions</a><br />\n<br />\n沈旭輝的分析文章: 聯合國維也納辦事處 任命曾偉雄 為總幹事？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://simonshen.blog/2019/07/22/%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%AD%E4%B9%9F%E7%B4%8D%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E8%99%95-%E4%BB%BB%E5%91%BD%E6%9B%BE%E5%81%89%E9%9B%84-%E7%82%BA%E7%B8%BD%E5%B9%B9%E4%BA%8B%EF%BC%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsimonshen.blog%2F2019%2F07%2F22%2F%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E4%25B9%259F%25E7%25B4%258D%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%2599%2595-%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%2591%25BD%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2581%2589%25E9%259B%2584-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E5%25B9%25B9%25E4%25BA%258B%25EF%25BC%259F%2F&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=de86fa56\" target=\"_blank\">https://simonshen.blog/2019/07/22/%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%AD%E4%B9%9F%E7%B4%8D%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E8%99%95-%E4%BB%BB%E5%91%BD%E6%9B%BE%E5%81%89%E9%9B%84-%E7%82%