{"pid":"8cc758c3651eedb548afae367277402a5769d280","tid":1390460,"uid":93905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:43:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff215c55ec00c2cd9fe7125a178edc98fc9858de","tid":1390460,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"白宮聯署仲廢過民建聯"},{"pid":"05d720b099cb59bcb0591c5a052439c7b859870f","tid":1390460,"uid":264074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:45:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3b018dffc751b49f3af8df5591101e4fea16bc49","tid":1390460,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:47:37.000Z","msg":"我哋由612開始爭取成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n不過，我哋從來冇討論過委員會由咩人去組成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人分析琴日中共為成立獨立調查委員會開綠燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋係時候開始討論當中嘅細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試過有法官判示威者以胸部襲警後，相信大家都明白香港有好多紅底法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以獨立調查委員會一定唔可以只係有本地法官組成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要嘅獨立調查委員會係<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>由國際專家、聯合國，甚至海牙軍事法庭嘅人組成</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拒絕港共自己人查自己人<br />\n<br />\n要由國際專家調查事件</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be963dc6a367b68c04ced30d79ad8aa078e1f